  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="KT366-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">kāvaṉ mikutikkaṇ vēṟupaṭṭa talaimakaḷatu vēṟupāṭu kaṇṭu “ivvēṟupāṭu
          eṟṟiṉāṉāyatu” (G2 stops here) eṉṟu cevili viṉāvat tōḻi kūṟiyatu. </p>


        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en">Spoken by the confidante who was asked by the
          foster-mother “of which kind is this change?”, having seen the change in HER, who changed
          during the increase in guarding. </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="KT366">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> pālvarait tamaitta lalla tavarvayiṟ</l>
          <l> cālpaḷan taṟitaṟ kiyāam yārō</l>
          <l> veṟiyāḷ kūṟavu mamaiyā ḷataṉṟalaip</l>
          <l> paiṅkaṇ māccuṉaip palpiṇi yaviḻnta</l>
          <l> vaḷḷitaḻ nīla nōkki yuḷḷakaip</l>
          <l> paḻuta kaṇṇa ḷākip</l>
          <l> paḻutaṉ ṟammaviv vāyiḻai tuṇivē.</l>


        </lg>

        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
          <l>Fate is set. Apart from what is allotted by it,</l>
          <l>who [are] we to measure [and] know the qualities in him?</l>
          <l rend="indent">Even when they say, “she [is] one for the Veṟi dance”, she is not quiet,
            [and] moreover,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">as one with tearful eyes,</l>
          <l rend="indent2">[her] mind tormented, looking at the blue of the full petals,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">which opened many fetters in the fresh-eyed ,</l>
          <l rend="indent9">big mountain pool,</l>
          <l>it is not a mistake, alas, the decision of this [woman</l>
          <l rend="indent9">with] choice jewels. </l>

          <lg type="alternate" sameAs="3b" resp="#TVG">
            <l>She is not quiet even when the Murukaṉ priestess pronounces</l>
            <l>[her diagnosis],</l>
          </lg>

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
